{
  "stem": "3964.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They knew better, we didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The luggage car was never hooked onto the train in Kassel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And our things, which were our worldly belongings, we no longer had.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was very cold that day, must've been about 10:00, 11 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was snowing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was snowing so badly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had never seen snow like that, although Gemunden, where I was born and raised, we had snow every winter.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it used to be a soft snow we used to have.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was snowing so hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was so cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were not prepared for that kind of weather.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They put us in columns and told us, if you do what you're told to do, you're going to be all right.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If not, what's going to-- what happened to this man, it's going to happen to you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And obviously, you know, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] not having [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] any idea how unhuman [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] humans can be-- and after all, they were Germans and so were we.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Well, when I say Germans, my father fought in the Second World War.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First World War.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father fought in the First World War, was on the Russian front, was wounded.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Had a-- [PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] a cross, Iron Cross I believe it's called, for his bravery in action.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My grandfather had been serving the Kaiser in 1890.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we were as German as Germans-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] as German as you can be.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sure, we were Jewish, but basically, you know, we're Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
